{"tid":2034973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳洲覺醒！為抗衡中國，澳洲急急向太平洋島國免費播映多部電視節目","createTime":"2020-05-25T14:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T13:35:44.000Z","uid":48040,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"24f84c6686422cb5c8dda01e581be8101e8ad911","tid":2034973,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》報導，澳洲周邊有多個島國，過去幾年，中國不斷拉攏這些島國，以獲得這些國家在聯合國的支持，並且對他們擁有的自然資源虎視眈眈。現在，澳洲也察覺到中國的野心，並且立即採取措施，重新建立澳洲和這些島國之間的聯盟關係。<br />\n澳洲現在採取的一個策略是，向這些島國提供澳洲電視台製作的綜藝節目以及劇集。澳洲外交部部長表示：「假如我們在電視屏幕上看到的是一樣的劇集，我相信這有利於澳洲和我們在太平洋上的盟友建立更加深入的聯繫。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/c26e4994-4313-41cd-8800-9a4a4e5a5ee4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fc26e4994-4313-41cd-8800-9a4a4e5a5ee4&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=b797c0b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/c26e4994-4313-41cd-8800-9a4a4e5a5ee4</a><br />\n《Australia unleashes &quot;Neighbors&quot; to counter China influence（澳洲向鄰國免費提供電視節目，抗衡中國的影響）》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亡羊補牢，為時未晚。但單單靠電視劇似乎......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n五毛話呢個channel的follower一定唔過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=aaa92d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a>"},{"pid":"c0948a791bd3ff4de1e2c02e93c4cbb3c0907be3","tid":2034973,"uid":179729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"澳洲！撐住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7a24a678bbf9fafd6655ae18197c338380efe1","tid":2034973,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0948a791bd3ff4de1e2c02e93c4cbb3c0907be3","tid":2034973,"uid":179729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc